        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/william_kelley/{size}/2314_2.png",
        "created_at": "2016-06-21T10:10:31.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I confess, I thought I had a pretty good handle on what Voerzio had gotten up to over the years, but I had no idea this wine existed. Looks like it\u2019s held up well. If you had to make a guess about the character of its \u00e9levage, what would it be?</p>",
