        "username": "Kirk.Grant",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/kirk.grant/{size}/1852_2.png",
        "created_at": "2016-06-21T10:18:50.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>A very cool wine\u2026and for me I can\u2019t imagine why he ripped up the Chardonnay.  While I\u2019ll admit that it\u2019s not always what I want to drink\u2026I do love the idea of getting some variety in the cellar and this sounds so unique that I can\u2019t imagine wanting to replace those vines with more Nebbiolo.</p>",
